### Login
POST http://localhost:50001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "admin",
  "senha": "admin123"
}

### Buscar todos (substituir TOKEN pelo valor retornado no login)
GET http://localhost:50001/cliente
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Buscar por ID
GET http://localhost:50001/cliente/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Inserir cliente
POST http://localhost:50001/cliente
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "profissao": "Desenvolvedor"
}

### Atualizar cliente
PUT http://localhost:50001/cliente/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "nome": "João Atualizado",
  "profissao": "Dev Senior"
}

### Deletar cliente
DELETE http://localhost:50001/cliente/2
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Teste sem token (deve retornar 401)
GET http://localhost:50001/cliente

### Teste credencial errada (deve retornar 401)
POST http://localhost:50001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "admin",
  "senha": "errada"
}
